quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"(Samwana) naboola mbu; “Ewe mwana wanje, olaboolelakhwo abasiani benyu amalooro koko ako tawe, bakhaba bario bakhututila. Toto Shetani khumundu ni omusuku owa habulafu."
  12,6,"Ne endio nilwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yetsa okhukhulobola mana akhwechesie okhukalula amalooro. Niyetsa okhwitsusia emikabo chichie khwiwe nende khulwibulo lwa Yaqub shingala yetsusilia bapapa bao emikabo, Ibrahim nende Is-haaq. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi ni Omumanyi, Owamachesi muno.""
  12,7,"Ne toto khu Yusufu nende abasiani babu bialiho ebimanyisio khubareebi."
  12,8,"Olwa baboola mbu; “Toto Yusuf nende Omusiani wabu bachamwa muno nende papa wefu, okhushila efwe, ne efwe khuli omukanda kwa amaani. Toto papa wefu ali mubukori bwa habulafu."
  12,9,"Yiree Yusufu nohomba mumusukune eshialo shia ehalee, kho obweni bwa papa wenyu bukalukhane okhuhenga enywesa. Ne nimumala kano, mulakalukhana okhuba abandu abalayi.""
  12,10,"Omubooli mubo naboola mbu; “Muleera Yusufu tawe, halali mumusukune mwitukho lirambi liamatsi, yetsa okhutolwa nende ababuranjila (balikhuluchendo), toto enywe nimuli abokhukhola.""
  12,11,"Nibaboola mbu; “Ewe papa wefu, shichila shina olakhusuubila khu Yusufu tawe? Toto efwe khumwenyelanga amalayi butswa.”"
  12,12,"Mulekhule atsie ninafu mutsuli, asangale nabaya, nafu toto khulamulinda.""
  12,13,"Naboola mbu; “Toto bilakhola okhubeelela enywe okhutsia ninaye, ne eritsanga eshisutse okhumulia nanyu nimukandaalile ehale ninaye.”"
  12,14,"Nibaboola mbu; “Eshisutse shiakhamulia shirie nafu khuli omukanda kwa amaani? Toto khuba khuli mubandu babula obukhala.”"